Class PSContentListItem

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.services.filter.data.PSFilterItem
      com.percussion.services.publisher.data.PSContentListItem
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPSFilterItem, Cloneable
public class PSContentListItem
extends com.percussion.services.filter.data.PSFilterItem

One item to add to the content list. This class is used by the template expander IPSTemplateExpander to communicate to the content list generator.

Author:
dougrand
